cdata.name: BlakeCoin
cdata.desc: BlakeCoin is based on the Blake-256 algorithm. The coin is merge mined and has a block reward, that varies based on the difficulty (25 coins + inflation(square root(difficulty * block height). The block time is 3 minutes and the block retargetting occurs every twenty successful hashing attempts. There are a total of 7 billion coins to be mined.
